Very good class.  She gives all the notes on the overhead.  Don't waste your time doing the readings, everything you need to know for the exams is in your notes.  She was very friendly and made the class interesting & fun, but she does expect you to study (it's not hard, it's all in your notes!!!)
She does skip steps. She does get lost in between the steps. Her helpfulness is almost 0 considering how hard the given subject is. I would like to see her solving some of the problems she assigns.

She's no-nonsense and tough, but an excellent prof. You'll be well prepared for the final. She explains everything clearly and her notes are complete (she never glosses over material). You'll feel like you got your money's worth out of her course.
